{"ts":"2026-06-04T07:55:53.767Z","author":"codex-sdk-continuation","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/8","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-04T07:55:53.767Z","author":"codex-sdk-continuation","text":"Gemini tombstone follow-up: projectAfterCommandItemSnapshot now returns an empty snapshot when metadata or metadata.id is absent, avoiding undefined identity fields for restored deleted-item tombstones."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-04T07:55:53.767Z"}],"before_hash":"b69a4a79d44916299c6c19a026fb227973b4331c3e490771678247633f0a0592","after_hash":"37d2f421e1d4ffacad6e59eef50080024c32c693494b3d7eaf7bb6b5eb793b5f"}
{"ts":"2026-06-04T08:18:22.639Z","author":"codex-sdk-continuation","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/9","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-04T08:18:22.639Z","author":"codex-sdk-continuation","text":"Gemini delete-snapshot follow-up: delete affected context now projects Object.keys(beforeDocument.metadata) into previous while preserving changed_fields=[deleted], so transition-aware hooks can inspect deleted item metadata such as title without parsing command result."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-04T08:18:22.639Z"}],"before_hash":"37d2f421e1d4ffacad6e59eef50080024c32c693494b3d7eaf7bb6b5eb793b5f","after_hash":"f58385aec0f84a1ce3f4c20b678a8d85c3001b6c718358c307d50512c148eef3"}
{"ts":"2026-06-04T08:40:05.699Z","author":"codex-sdk-continuation","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/10","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-04T08:40:05.699Z","author":"codex-sdk-continuation","text":"Gemini defensive follow-up: recordAfterCommandAffectedItem now ignores nullish items, and projectAfterCommandItemSnapshot now returns seeded metadata when changedFields is not an array and skips non-string changed-field entries before string normalization."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-04T08:40:05.699Z"}],"before_hash":"f58385aec0f84a1ce3f4c20b678a8d85c3001b6c718358c307d50512c148eef3","after_hash":"029ce73230833bb97f442a9416c7da4f563f0aa1cfaca753848152c45de17d54"}
{"ts":"2026-06-04T09:01:33.462Z","author":"codex-sdk-continuation","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/11","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-04T09:01:33.462Z","author":"codex-sdk-continuation","text":"Gemini afterCommand failure follow-up: runAndClearAfterCommandHooks now catches afterCommand hook failures, prints a warning, preserves cleanup in finally, and avoids masking the primary command outcome."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-04T09:01:33.462Z"}],"before_hash":"029ce73230833bb97f442a9416c7da4f563f0aa1cfaca753848152c45de17d54","after_hash":"503ecd406f0ebfa99703b41c1ddca6b67dfa29f9adb4b975cf2a559fbe34e310"}
{"ts":"2026-06-04T09:22:58.699Z","author":"codex-sdk-continuation","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/12","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-04T09:22:58.699Z","author":"codex-sdk-continuation","text":"Codex review follow-up: afterCommand hook warnings returned by runAfterCommandHooks are now surfaced in normal stderr output instead of only profile diagnostics, while profile mode keeps the detailed profile hook_warnings line."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-04T09:22:58.699Z"}],"before_hash":"503ecd406f0ebfa99703b41c1ddca6b67dfa29f9adb4b975cf2a559fbe34e310","after_hash":"09bca42c5a680378e65a9420b5b5f2ed0e8d024599ab7f330de052b0053c6f76"}
{"ts":"2026-06-04T09:44:23.574Z","author":"codex-sdk-continuation","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/13","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-04T09:44:23.574Z","author":"codex-sdk-continuation","text":"Codex JSON-mode follow-up: normal afterCommand warning surfacing is now suppressed when --json is active so JSON error stderr remains parseable; profile diagnostics remain profile-scoped."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-04T09:44:23.574Z"}],"before_hash":"09bca42c5a680378e65a9420b5b5f2ed0e8d024599ab7f330de052b0053c6f76","after_hash":"e956aadf450a637318927dd9f9f3002b57258ceca2c1d2531913c531c94765e9"}
